		<div class="details">
			<span class="by"><span class="byby">by </span><a href="//slashdot.org/~ThumpBzztZoom">ThumpBzztZoom</a>  <span class="uid"><a href="//slashdot.org/~ThumpBzztZoom">( 6976422 )</a></span></a></span><span class="writes" style="display:none"> writes:</span> 
			<span class="otherdetails" id="comment_otherdetails_64448488">		
		on Saturday May 04, 2024 @10:24PM (<span class="ind"></span><a href="//idle.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23312754&amp;cid=64448488">#64448488</a>)
		<small> </small>
